    proj‚Üê‚àò.=‚ç®‚ç≥4
    view‚Üê‚àò.=‚ç®‚ç≥4
    proj_view‚Üêview+.√óproj
    time‚Üê0

    toggle_ui‚Üê0
    info_scope‚Üê‚ç¨
    text_base‚Üê(
    'Hello ‚åΩ''dlrow'''
    'Chunks Loaded: '
